="00:09.612">torrid</span> <span begin="00:09.612" end="00:10.392">affair</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">亚历山大·汉密尔顿有一段火辣的私情</span></p><p begin="00:10.502" end="00:12.625" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L4"><span begin="00:10.502" end="00:10.718">And</span> <span begin="00:10.718" end="00:10.918">he</span> <span begin="00:10.918" end="00:11.118">wrote</span> <span begin="00:11.118" end="00:11.310">it</span> <span begin="00:11.310" end="00:11.723">down</span> <span begin="00:11.723" end="00:12.110">right</span> <span begin="00:12.110" end="00:12.625">there</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">而且他居然亲笔把它写了下来</span></p><p begin="00:12.564" end="00:13.844" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L5"><span begin="00:12.564" end="00:13.844">Highlights!</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">精彩片段选读！</span></p><p begin="00:13.660" end="00:16.970" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L6"><span begin="00:13.660" end="00:13.863">The</span> <span begin="00:13.863" end="00:14.119">charge</span> <span begin="00:14.119" end="00:14.593">against</span> <span begin="00:14.593" end="00:14.767">me</span> <span begin="00:14.767" end="00:14.948">is</span> <span begin="00:14.948" end="00:15.089">a</span> <span begin="00:15.089" end="00:15.564">connection</span> <span begin="00:15.564" end="00:15.756">with</span> <span begin="00:15.756" end="00:15.924">one</span> <span begin="00:15.924" end="00:16.359">James</span> <span begin="00:16.359" end="00:16.970">Reynolds</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">“针对我的指控是与一位詹姆斯·雷诺兹有染</span></p><p begin="00:17.113" end="00:19.925" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L7"><span begin="00:17.113" end="00:17.310">For</span> <span begin="00:17.310" end="00:18.105">purposes</span> <span begin="00:18.105" end="00:18.276">of</span> <span begin="00:18.276" end="00:18.889">improper</span> <span begin="00:18.889" end="00:19.925">speculation</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">目的是为了进行不正当的（公款）投机”</span></p><p begin="00:20.092" end="00:23.189" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L8"><span begin="00:20.092" end="00:20.311">My</span> <span begin="00:20.311" end="00:20.529">real</span> <span begin="00:20.529" end="00:20.839">crime</span> <span begin="00:20.839" end="00:20.980">is</span> <span begin="00:20.980" end="00:21.100">an</span> <span begin="00:21.100" end="00:21.639">amorous</span> <span begin="00:21.639" end="00:22.252">connection</span> <span begin="00:22.252" end="00:22.447">with</span> <span begin="00:22.447" end="00:22.631">his</span> <span begin="00:22.631" end="00:23.189">wife</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">“我真正的罪名是与他的妻子有染</span></p><p begin="00:23.337" end="00:27.522" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L9"><span begin="00:23.337" end="00:23.508">For</span> <span begin="00:23.508" end="00:23.652">a</span> <span begin="00:23.652" end="00:24.278">considerable</span> <span begin="00:24.278" end="00:24.798">time</span> <span begin="00:24.841" end="00:24.990">with</span> <span begin="00:24.990" end="00:25.278">his</span> <span begin="00:25.278" end="00:25.857">knowing</span> <span begin="00:25.857" end="00:26.569">consent</span> <span begin="00:26.569" end="00:27.522">(Damn!)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">持续了相当长的时间，且经过了他知情后的同意”（天呐！）</span></p><p begin="00:27.421" end="00:29.203" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L10"><span begin="00:27.421" end="00:27.578">I</span> <span begin="00:27.578" end="00:27.792">had</span> <span begin="00:27.792" end="00:28.186">frequent</span> <span begin="00:28.186" end="00:28.592">meetings</span> <span begin="00:28.592" end="00:28.781">with</span> <span begin="00:28.781" end="00:29.203">her</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">“我与她频繁幽会</span></p><p begin="00:29.387" end="00:31.264" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L11"><span begin="00:29.387" end="00:29.758">Most</span> <span begin="00:29.758" end="00:29.894">of</span> <span begin="00:29.894" end="00:30.108">them</span> <span begin="00:30.108" end="00:30.208">at</span> <span begin="00:30.208" end="00:30.414">my</span> <span begin="00:30.414" end="00:30.635">own</span> <span begin="00:30.635" end="00:31.264">house</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">大多数时间是在我自己的家里”</span></p><p begin="00:31.003" end="00:33.706" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L12"><span begin="00:31.003" end="00:31.210">At</span> <span begin="00:31.210" end="00:31.310">his</span> <span begin="00:31.310" end="00:31.502">own</span> <span begin="00:31.502" end="00:31.846">house?</span> <span begin="00:31.846" end="00:31.979">At</span> <span begin="00:31.979" end="00:32.112">his</span> <span begin="00:32.112" end="00:32.326">own</span> <span begin="00:32.326" end="00:32.729">house</span> <span begin="00:32.883" end="00:33.706">(Damn!)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在他自己家里？在他自己家里（太渣了！）</span></p><p begin="00:33.549" end="00:35.076" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L13"><span begin="00:33.549" end="00:33.792">Mrs.</span> <span begin="00:33.792" end="00:34.336">Hamilton</span> <span begin="00:34.336" end="00:34.456">with</span> <span begin="00:34.456" end="00:34.666">our</span> <span begin="00:34.666" end="00:35.076">children</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">“当时汉密尔顿夫人正带着我们的孩子们</span></p><p begin="00:35.186" end="00:37.733" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L14"><span begin="00:35.186" end="00:35.402">Being</span> <span begin="00:35.402" end="00:36.042">absent</span> <span begin="00:36.042" end="00:36.162">on</span> <span begin="00:36.162" end="00:36.298">a</span> <span begin="00:36.298" end="00:36.642">visit</span> <span begin="00:36.642" end="00:36.885">to</span> <span begin="00:36.885" end="00:37.050">her</span> <span begin="00:37.050" end="00:37.733">father</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">回娘家探望她的父亲”</span></p><p begin="00:37.843" end="00:40.481" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L15"><span begin="00:37.843" end="00:38.473">No</span> <span begin="00:38.729" end="00:40.481">(Boo!)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">不会吧（太差劲了！）</span></p><p begin="00:39.108" end="00:40.507" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L16"><span begin="00:39.108" end="00:39.407">Have</span> <span begin="00:39.407" end="00:39.604">you</span> <span begin="00:39.604" end="00:39.961">read</span> <span begin="00:39.961" end="00:40.507">this?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你读过这个了吗？</span></p><p begin="00:40.008" end="00:42.333" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L17"><span begin="00:40.008" end="00:40.312">Well,</span> <span begin="00:40.312" end="00:40.517">he's</span> <span begin="00:40.517" end="00:40.845">never</span> <span begin="00:40.845" end="00:41.163">gon'</span> <span begin="00:41.163" end="00:41.357">be</span> <span begin="00:41.357" end="00:41.971">president</span> <span begin="00:41.971" end="00:42.333">now</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">嘿，他现在永远也当不成总统了</span></p><p begin="00:42.200" end="00:43.949" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L18"><span begin="00:42.200" end="00:42.520">Never</span> <span begin="00:42.520" end="00:42.805">gon'</span> <span begin="00:42.805" end="00:42.989">be</span> <span begin="00:42.989" end="00:43.549">president</span> <span begin="00:43.549" end="00:43.949">now</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">永远当不成总统了</span></p><p begin="00:43.894" end="00:45.666" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L19"><span begin="00:43.894" end="00:44.149">Never</span> <span begin="00:44.149" end="00:44.448">gon'</span> <span begin="00:44.448" end="00:44.651">be</span> <span begin="00:44.651" end="00:45.333">president</span> <span begin="00:45.333" end="00:45.666">now</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">永远当不成总统了</span></p><p begin="00:45.532" end="00:47.304" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L20"><span begin="00:45.532" end="00:45.883">Never</span> <span begin="00:45.883" end="00:46.152">gon'</span> <span begin="00:46.152" end="00:46.357">be</span> <span begin="00:46.357" end="00:46.965">president</span> <span begin="00:46.965" end="00:47.304">now</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">永远当不成总统了</span></p><p begin="00:47.166" end="00:49.021" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L21"><span begin="00:47.166" end="00:47.528">Never</span> <span begin="00:47.528" end="00:47.861">gon'</span> <span begin="00:47.861" end="00:48.021">be</span> <span begin="00:48.021" end="00:48.691">president</span> <span begin="00:48.691" end="00:49.021">now</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">永远当不成总统了</span></p><p begin="00:48.900" end="00:50.701" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L22"><span begin="00:48.900" end="00:49.243">Never</span> <span begin="00:49.243" end="00:49.536">gon'</span> <span begin="00:49.536" end="00:49.736">be</span> <span begin="00:49.736" end="00:50.344">president</span> <span begin="00:50.344" end="00:50.701">now</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">永远当不成总统了</span></p><p begin="00:50.448" end="00:52.098" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L23"><span begin="00:50.448" end="00:50.696">That's</span> <span begin="00:50.696" end="00:50.880">one</span> <span begin="00:50.880" end="00:51.045">less</span> <span begin="00:51.045" end="00:51.240">thing</span> <span begin="00:51.240" end="00:51.408">to</span> <span begin="00:51.408" end="00:51.699">worry</span> <span begin="00:51.699" end="00:52.098">about</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">那就少了一件让人担心的事了</span></p><p begin="00:52.142" end="00:54.050" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L24"><span begin="00:52.142" end="00:52.339">That's</span> <span begin="00:52.339" end="00:52.529">one</span> <span begin="00:52.529" end="00:52.713">less</span> <span begin="00:52.713" end="00:52.907">thing</span> <span begin="00:52.907" end="00:53.067">to</span> <span begin="00:53.067" end="00:53.337">worry</span> <span begin="00:53.337" end="00:54.050">about</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">那就少了一件让人担心的事了</span></p><p begin="00:55.394" end="00:56.850" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L25"><span begin="00:55.394" end="00:55.645">I</span> <span begin="00:55.645" end="00:55.895">came</span> <span begin="00:55.895" end="00:56.045">as</span> <span begin="00:56.045" end="00:56.181">soon</span> <span begin="00:56.181" end="00:56.311">as</span> <span begin="00:56.311" end="00:56.415">I</span> <span begin="00:56.415" end="00:56.850">heard</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我一听到消息就立刻赶过来了</span></p><p begin="00:56.830" end="00:57.778" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L26"><span begin="00:56.830" end="00:57.778">What?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">什么？</span></p><p begin="00:57.107" end="00:58.307" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L27"><span begin="00:57.107" end="00:57.686">Angelic</span><span begin="00:57.686" end="00:58.307">a</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">安杰莉卡</span></p><p begin="00:58.200" end="01:00.553" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L28"><span begin="00:58.200" end="00:58.472">All</span> <span begin="00:58.472" end="00:58.616">the</span> <span begin="00:58.616" end="00:58.867">way</span> <span begin="00:58.867" end="00:59.053">from</span> <span begin="00:59.053" end="00:59.709">London?</span> <span begin="00:59.939" end="01:00.553">Damn</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">一路从伦敦赶回来的？真行啊</span></p><p begin="01:00.613" end="01:01.871" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L29"><span begin="01:00.613" end="01:01.304">Angelica,</span> <span begin="01:01.304" end="01:01.560">thank</span> <span begin="01:01.560" end="01:01.871">God</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">安杰莉卡，感谢上帝</span></p><p begin="01:01.871" end="01:03.058" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L30"><span begin="01:01.871" end="01:02.223">Someone</span> <span begin="01:02.223" end="01:02.362">who</span> <span begin="01:02.362" end="01:03.058">understands</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">终于有个能理解的人</span></p><p begin="01:03.058" end="01:04.807" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L31"><span begin="01:03.058" end="01:03.162">What</span> <span begin